<title>ạnạ jạy lk ạ̉nạ rạjʿ lyk</title>
<lyrics>[C1]
   ạlqrạr:- ạnạ jạy lk ạ̉nạ rạjʿ lyk
   bạ̉ʿtrf ạ̹ny ạḥtjt ạ̹lyk
   ʿmr ḥyạẗ ạlbʿd mạ tsẖbʿ
   qlby ạsẖtạq ysẖbʿ byk

[V1]
 1- ạ̉nt wʿdt wqlt tʿạl
 wạrmy bḥmlk rạḥ trtạḥ
 ậdy ạlḥml wậdy ạlḥạlẗ
 wạ̉nạ qdạmk kly jrạḥ

[V2]
 2- mḥtạj lk mḥtạj tdạwyny
 mḥtạj lk mḥtạj lạ̉ydyk
 tgẖsl qlby wtlms ʿyny
 trsm fyã ḥyạẗ trḍyk

[V3]
 3- ạ̉nạ mḥtạj lk tkẖlq fyã
 qlb jdyd bạlnʿmẗ ykwn
 rạḥẗ lqlbk dạymạaⁿ fyã
 qlb yrnm mhmạ ykwn

[V4]
 4- rd ly frḥ kẖlạṣk ly
 rd lʿyny ḥyạẗ ạlnwr
 rd lqlby ḥḍwrk fy
 ạ̉rjʿ ạ̉rnm wạ̉nạ msrwr</lyrics>
</song>